quran[4{c,v,t}:
6,91,"un logon ne Allah ka bohat ghalat andaza lagaya jab kaha ke Allah ne kisi bashar par kuch nazil nahi kya hai un se pucho, phir woh kitaab jisay moose laya tha, jo tamam insanon ke liye roshni aur hadaayat thi, jisay tum Parah Parah kar ke rakhtay ho, kuch dikhata ho aur bohat kuch chhupa jatay ho, aur jis ke zareya se tum ko woh ilm diya gaya jo nah tumhe haasil tha aur nah tumahray baap dada ko, aakhir uss ka nazil karne wala kon tha? bas itna keh do ke Allah , phir unhen apni Daleel bazyon se khailnay ke liye chore do"
6,92,( usi kitaab ki terhan ) yeh aik kitaab hai jisay hum ne nazil kya hai barri kher o barket wali hai uss cheez ki tasdeeq karti hai jo is se pehlay aayi thi aur is liye nazil ki gayi hai ke is ke zareya se tum bustiyon ke iss markaz ( yani mecca ) aur is ke atraaf mein rehne walon ko mutnabba karo jo lau g akhirat ko mantay hain woh is kitaab par imaan laatay hain aur un ka haal yeh hai ke apni namazon ki pabandi karte hain
6,93,"aur uss shakhs se bara zalim aur kon hoga jo Allah par jhoota bohtan gharrey, ya kahe ke mujh par wahi aayi haidar-aa-n hala-n kehہ is par koi wahi nazil nah ki gayi ho, ya jo Allah ki nazil kardah cheez ke muqaabla mein kahe ke mein bhi aisi cheez nazil kar ke dikha dun ga? kash tum zaalmon ko is haalat mein dekh sakuu jab ke woh sukrat -e- mout mein dubkian kha rahay hotay hain aur farishtay haath barha barha kar keh rahay hotay hain ke"" lao, nikalu apni jaan, aaj tumhe unn baton ki Padaash mein zillat ka azaab diya jaye ga jo tum Allah par tohmat rakh kar na-haq bakka karte thay aur uss ki ayaat ke muqaabla mein sar kashi dikhata thay """
6,94,"( aur Allah farmaiye ga )"" lau ab tum waisay hi tan tanha hamaray samnay haazir hogaye jaissa hum ne tumhe pehli martaba akela peda kya tha, jo kuch hum ne tumhe duniya mein diya tha woh sab tum peechay chore aeye ho, aur ab hum tumahray sath tumahray unn safarshiyun ko bhi nahi dekhte jin ke mutaliq tum samajte thay ke tumahray kaam bananay mein un ka bhi kuch hissa hai, tumahray aapas ke sab raabtey toot gay aur woh sab tum se gum hogaye jin ka tum zeam rakhtay thay """
